summary: The customer wants to know the status of their package. IC Customer Service representative assures the customer that they will look into the issue and get back to them as soon as possible. The customer's package was stuck at the factory in Bangalore and they were provided with the address where it could be located. The customer also mentioned experiencing side effects from using the product and wants to know what they can do to resolve the issue. The customer is informed that a new packet will be sent to them as soon as possible.
speaker_a_summary: Kijie wishes to register a complaint about a product and speak to a concerned agent regarding the issue. The customer service representative creates a ticket for the complaint and arranges for a new packet to be sent to Kijie so that the agent can test the product and resolve the issue. The representative informs Kijie that the agent will visit the factory, locate the specific batch number of the product, and then deliver a new packet to Kijie's residence. The agent will also collect the defective product for testing and troubleshooting purposes. Kijie is informed that the agent will solve the problem and provide a new packet as a replacement. The call ends with Kijie confirming that they will remain on hold for a few minutes until the agent arrives.
speaker_b_summary: The narrator is having a heated argument with someone over the phone regarding a missing packet of items. The narrator repeatedly asks why the packet was taken away and insists that they have already provided all the necessary information, such as the batch number, bar code, and other details. They mention that there are issues with the main packet and that there are two side effects, one of which they experienced themselves. The narrator also describes the poor hygiene and unsafe conditions at the factory where the packets were manufactured and wonders why the other party is not listening to them. They demand the address of the plant so they can inspect it. The narrator also mentions their love for their daughter and that they will go to any length to help her. Finally, they mention that they have already lost everything but still intend to go to the factory.
cohere_points:
- Customer wants to know where his package is and why it hasn't been delivered
- Agent is trying to help the customer but needs more information and asks the customer to send photos of the batch number and bar code
- Agent wants to send the customer a new packet but needs to investigate where the original packet went 
- There seems to be a discrepancy with the packet being sent to the factory for testing and the agent needs to register the customers complaint 
- Agent is trying to help the customer but needs more information
